[[The Hippy Camp]] is an adventure [[locations|location]] found in [[The Mysterious Island of Mystery]]. If your main stat isn't high enough, you'll see the following message:

:Too... Many... Hippies...

:Not... strong enough... To go on...

:(You must have at least 30 $Stat to adventure here.)

Visiting the Camp in the [[Filthy Hippy Disguise]] and [[ War Hippy Fatigues]] [[:Category:Outfits|outfit]] will yield a different set of adventures from those while not disguised.

Once you start the [[Mysterious Island Quest]], you will get a different set of adventures. See [[The Hippy Camp (Verge of War)]] or [[The Hippy Camp (Wartime)]].

